&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marty Supreme&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The film &lt;strong&gt;Marty Supreme&lt;/strong&gt; tied the BAFTA record for the most losses at a single ceremony.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Despite receiving an impressive 11 nominations, it did not win a single award (0-for-11).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Comprehensive BAFTA 2026 Awards Reference&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;11&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;Major Awards &amp;amp; Acting Honors&lt;/b&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;Best Film &amp;amp; Best Director:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;27&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;Paul Thomas Anderson&lt;/b&gt; for &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;52&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;52&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;One Battle After Another&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;Outstanding British Film:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;26&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;26&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;Hamnet&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; (Produced by Chlo&amp;eacute; Zhao, Liza Marshall, et al.).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;Best Leading Actor:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;20&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;Robert Aramayo&lt;/b&gt; (&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;36&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;I Swear&lt;/i&gt;). He made history by also winning the public-voted &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;95&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;EE Rising Star Award&lt;/b&gt; in the same year.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;Best Leading Actress:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;22&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;Jessie Buckley&lt;/b&gt; (&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;38&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;Hamnet&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,4,0&quot;&gt;Best Supporting Actor:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;23&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,4,0&quot;&gt;Sean Penn&lt;/b&gt; (&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;34&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,4,0&quot;&gt;One Battle After Another&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,5,0&quot;&gt;Best Supporting Actress:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;25&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,5,0&quot;&gt;Wunmi Mosaku&lt;/b&gt; (&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;39&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,5,0&quot;&gt;Sinners&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;Screenplay &amp;amp; Genre Awards&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot;&gt;Best Original Screenplay:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;26&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot;&gt;Ryan Coogler&lt;/b&gt; for &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;43&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;43&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot;&gt;Sinners&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot;&gt;Best Adapted Screenplay:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;25&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot;&gt;Paul Thomas Anderson&lt;/b&gt; for &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;50&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;50&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot;&gt;One Battle After Another&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot;&gt;Best Children&amp;#39;s &amp;amp; Family Film:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;31&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;31&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot;&gt;Boong&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;. Backed by Excel Entertainment, this Manipuri-language film made history as the &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;117&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot;&gt;first Indian film&lt;/b&gt; to win a BAFTA in this category.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;7,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,3,0&quot;&gt;Best Animated Film:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;20&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;20&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,3,0&quot;&gt;Zootopia 2&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;7,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,4,0&quot;&gt;Best Film Not in the English Language:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;39&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;39&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,4,0&quot;&gt;Sentimental Value&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;7,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,5,0&quot;&gt;Best Documentary:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;18&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;18&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;7,5,0&quot;&gt;Mr Nobody Against Putin&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;Technical &amp;amp; Special Honors&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot;&gt;Technical Sweeps:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;18&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;18&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot;&gt;Frankenstein&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; won three awards for &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;52&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot;&gt;Production Design&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;71&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot;&gt;Costume Design&lt;/b&gt;, and &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;91&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot;&gt;Make Up &amp;amp; Hair&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1,0&quot;&gt;Best Original Score:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;21&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1,0&quot;&gt;Ludwig G&amp;ouml;ransson&lt;/b&gt; for &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;42&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;42&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1,0&quot;&gt;Sinners&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; (Ryan Coogler accepted the award on his behalf, joking he was busy with &amp;quot;a small independent film called &lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;155&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1,0&quot;&gt;The Odyssey&lt;/i&gt;&amp;quot;).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;9,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,2,0&quot;&gt;Best Sound:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;12&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;12&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,2,0&quot;&gt;F1&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;9,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,3,0&quot;&gt;Best Special Visual Effects:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;29&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;29&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,3,0&quot;&gt;Avatar: Fire and Ash&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;9,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,4,0&quot;&gt;BAFTA Fellowship:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;18&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,4,0&quot;&gt;Donna Langley&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;9,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,5,0&quot;&gt;Outstanding British Contribution to Cinema:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;44&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;9,5,0&quot;&gt;Clare Binns&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;10&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;10&quot;&gt;Historic Milestones&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot;&gt;One Battle After Another&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; set a BAFTA record for the &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;52&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot;&gt;most nominations (14)&lt;/b&gt; and led the night with &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;97&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot;&gt;6 wins&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot;&gt;Hamnet&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; became the &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;18&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot;&gt;most-nominated film by a female director&lt;/b&gt; (Chlo&amp;eacute; Zhao) in BAFTA history with 11 nominations.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,2,0&quot;&gt;Sinners&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; became the &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;19&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,2,0&quot;&gt;most-nominated and most-awarded film by a Black director&lt;/b&gt; (Ryan Coogler), earning 13 nominations and 3 wins.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,3,0&quot;&gt;Marty Supreme&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; tied the record for the &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;38&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;11,3,0&quot;&gt;most losses&lt;/b&gt; at a single ceremony, going 0-for-11.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pradhan Mantri Skilling and Employability Transformation through Upgraded ITIs (PM-SETU).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Prime Minister announced the establishment of the India&amp;ndash;France National Centre of Excellence in Aeronautics at Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh under the PM-SETU scheme.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Centre will be established at National Skill Training Institute (NSTI), Kanpur in collaboration with the Government of France.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It will focus on advanced skill training in aeronautics, MRO, airport operations and defence manufacturing.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The initiative builds upon the India&amp;ndash;France Strategic Partnership and a 2025 MoU in skill development and vocational training.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;PM-SETU has an overall outlay of ₹60,000 crore to upgrade 1000 ITIs across India.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PM-SETU:&lt;/strong&gt; A flagship scheme of the Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship aimed at modernising ITIs and aligning training with industry requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;National Centre of Excellence (NCoE):&lt;/strong&gt; A specialised institution designed to deliver high-quality, industry-integrated vocational education and advanced skill training.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Maintenance, Repair and Overhaul (MRO):&lt;/strong&gt; Services related to inspection, repair and maintenance of aircraft and aviation equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India&amp;ndash;France Strategic Partnership:&lt;/strong&gt; A bilateral framework enhancing cooperation in defence, space, technology, skill development and innovation sectors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;Ranvir Sachdeva.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ranvir Sachdeva&lt;/strong&gt;, an 8-year-old coder, became the &lt;strong&gt;youngest keynote speaker&lt;/strong&gt; at the India AI Impact Summit 2026.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The summit was held at &lt;strong&gt;Bharat Mandapam, New Delhi&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Highlights&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;He spoke about linking &lt;strong&gt;ancient Indian philosophies&lt;/strong&gt; with &lt;strong&gt;modern Artificial Intelligence&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Discussed India&amp;rsquo;s AI development approach and global AI strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Shared his use case of a recently released &lt;strong&gt;Indian AI model&lt;/strong&gt; and contributions toward AI literacy.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Met global tech leaders including &lt;strong&gt;Sundar Pichai (Google CEO)&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Sam Altman (OpenAI CEO)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;13th edition of Exercise MILAN-2026&lt;/strong&gt; was inaugurated at &lt;strong&gt;Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The event was inaugurated by &lt;strong&gt;Defence Minister Rajnath Singh&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Highlights&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;MILAN-2026 is the &lt;strong&gt;largest and most inclusive edition&lt;/strong&gt; to date, with participation from &lt;strong&gt;74 nations&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The exercise is conducted under the &lt;strong&gt;Eastern Naval Command&lt;/strong&gt; in Visakhapatnam.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Aims to enhance &lt;strong&gt;interoperability, professional competence, and maritime cooperation&lt;/strong&gt; among participating navies.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Includes joint exercises, professional exchanges, and cultural interactions to strengthen trust and coordinated responses to maritime challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;South Africa&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The 2026 ICC Men&amp;rsquo;s T20 World Cup concluded with India defending their title against New Zealand.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
