questions.statement:
Which among the following countries&amp;#39; leaders attended the AI Impact Summit 2026?&lt;br /&gt;
1. President of France&lt;br /&gt;
2. President of Slovakia&lt;br /&gt;
3. President of Cyprus&lt;br /&gt;
4. President of UAE&lt;br /&gt;
5. President of Sri Lanka&lt;br /&gt;
Answer using the codes below:

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1, 2 and 5.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Several global leaders including the Presidents of France, Slovak Republic, and Sri Lanka visited India to attend the AI Impact Summit 2026 held in New Delhi.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;H.E. Mr. Emmanuel Macron, President of the French Republic, attended the AI Impact Summit 2026 and arrived in India on 17th and 18th February 2026.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;H.E. Mr. Peter Pellegrini, President of the Slovak Republic, attended the summit and arrived on 18th February 2026.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;H.E. Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake, President of the Democratic Republic of Sri Lanka, attended the summit and arrived on 17th February 2026.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Crown Prince of Abu Dhabi represented the UAE, not the President, and no leader from Cyprus attended the summit.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Impact Summit 2026&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The summit was held in New Delhi in February 2026.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;It brought together Presidents, Prime Ministers, Vice Presidents, and global institutional leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The summit aimed to strengthen global cooperation in Artificial Intelligence governance and innovation.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;It highlighted India&amp;#39;s leadership role in shaping global AI development.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Participation of UAE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The UAE was represented by H.E. Sheikh Khaled Bin Mohamed Bin Zayed Al Nahyan.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;He attended in his capacity as Crown Prince of Abu Dhabi.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The President of UAE did not attend the summit.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global Representation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Multiple heads of state including &lt;strong&gt;Presidents &lt;/strong&gt;of &lt;strong&gt;Brazil, Switzerland, Estonia, France, Serbia, and Slovakia&lt;/strong&gt; attended.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Several &lt;strong&gt;Prime Ministers&lt;/strong&gt; including those of&lt;strong&gt; Finland, Netherlands, Mauritius, and Bhutan &lt;/strong&gt;also participated.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;International organisations such as IMF and United Nations were represented by their top leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tina and Milo.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Meet the Mascots&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Characters:&lt;/strong&gt; The official mascots for Milano Cortina 2026 (6 to 22 Feb 2026) Winter Olympics and Paralympics 2026 (6 to 15 March 2026) are two cheerful &lt;strong&gt;stoats&lt;/strong&gt; (ermines) named &lt;strong&gt;Tina and Milo&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tina:&lt;/strong&gt; The lighter-colored stoat is the mascot for the &lt;strong&gt;Olympic Winter Games&lt;/strong&gt;. Her name is derived from &lt;strong&gt;Cortina&lt;/strong&gt; d&amp;rsquo;Ampezzo.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Milo:&lt;/strong&gt; Her younger brother, the darker-colored stoat, is the mascot for the &lt;strong&gt;Paralympic Winter Games&lt;/strong&gt;. His name is derived from &lt;strong&gt;Milano&lt;/strong&gt; (Milan).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Symbolism&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resilience:&lt;/strong&gt; Stoats were chosen because they are resilient animals capable of adapting to harsh winter conditions in the Italian Alps.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inclusivity:&lt;/strong&gt; Milo is depicted with only one paw, symbolizing &lt;strong&gt;diversity and the ability to overcome obstacles&lt;/strong&gt;, which aligns with the spirit of the Paralympics.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative Origin:&lt;/strong&gt; The designs were inspired by ideas submitted by school children from across Italy, showcasing a bottom-up approach to the Games&amp;#39; identity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (0, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Quick Facts&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tina&amp;#39;s Motto:&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;quot;Dream big!&amp;quot;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Milo&amp;#39;s Motto:&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;quot;Obstacles are steps!&amp;quot;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The duo is often accompanied by &amp;quot;The Flo&amp;quot; (six little snowdrops), representing the values of friendship and teamwork.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gamini.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In February 2026, the South African cheetah &lt;strong&gt;Gamini&lt;/strong&gt; gave birth to three cubs at Kuno National Park in Madhya Pradesh.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;This was reported as the &lt;strong&gt;9th successful cheetah litter&lt;/strong&gt; on Indian soil since the start of the reintroduction project.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Facts&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Gamini is a &lt;strong&gt;second-time mother&lt;/strong&gt;, and her new &amp;quot;little sprinters&amp;quot; have significantly boosted the population count.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Union Environment Minister Bhupender Yadav described this as a &amp;quot;roaring new chapter&amp;quot; for Kuno.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Population Breakdown&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Total Cheetahs in India:&lt;/strong&gt; 38 (as of Feb 18, 2026).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Indian-born surviving cubs:&lt;/strong&gt; 27.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;This population includes both the surviving translocated adults and the cubs born in Kuno National Park.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Robert Aramayo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Robert Aramayo&lt;/strong&gt; pulled off a historic double victory at the 2026 ceremony.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;He won the award for Best Leading Actor for his role in &lt;em&gt;I Swear&lt;/em&gt; and also won the publicly-voted EE Rising Star Award.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Comprehensive BAFTA 2026 Awards Reference&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;11&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;Major Awards &amp;amp; Acting Honors&lt;/b&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;Best Film &amp;amp; Best Director:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;27&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;Paul Thomas Anderson&lt;/b&gt; for &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;52&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;52&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;One Battle After Another&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;Outstanding British Film:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;26&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;26&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;Hamnet&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; (Produced by Chlo&amp;eacute; Zhao, Liza Marshall, et al.).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;Best Leading Actor:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;20&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;Robert Aramayo&lt;/b&gt; (&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;36&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;I Swear&lt;/i&gt;). He made history by also winning the public-voted &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;95&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;EE Rising Star Award&lt;/b&gt; in the same year.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;Best Leading Actress:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;22&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;Jessie Buckley&lt;/b&gt; (&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;38&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;Hamnet&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,4,0&quot;&gt;Best Supporting Actor:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;23&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,4,0&quot;&gt;Sean Penn&lt;/b&gt; (&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;34&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,4,0&quot;&gt;One Battle After Another&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,5,0&quot;&gt;Best Supporting Actress:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;25&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,5,0&quot;&gt;Wunmi Mosaku&lt;/b&gt; (&lt;i data-index-in-node=&quot;39&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,5,0&quot;&gt;Sinners&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
